---
title: Indian-Spiced Veggie Burgers with Beyond Meat® and Sweet Potato Wedges
description: Shake up your at-home burger game! These beautifully spiced Beyond Meat® burgers get a dose of sweetness from our fig spread. The gentle tartness of the yogurt dip pulls double duty: It adds a layer of flavour to the burger's spring greens and serves as a delicious dip for earthy sweet potatoes.
